三人得之者，亦同。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e9%87%91%e7%b0%a1%2c19%2c20220218%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,金簡,19,20220218,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"金簡","JNO":"19","JDATE":"20220218","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}